{"tid":1814913,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"全世界係咪得香港人先會有「兩個」名？","createTime":"2020-01-07T06:45:54.000Z","updateTime":"2020-01-07T07:48:52.000Z","uid":78947,"like":4,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"b9e8a724f0c5e064439830e865e7e89a9f8ea028","tid":1814913,"uid":78947,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:45:54.000Z","msg":"其他非英語國民嘅英文名名都係按母語照譯: 安倍晉三 abe shinzo<br />\n<br />\n但香港人個英文名通常都唔關中文名事<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3fd8c0d33c727187d64a1e113d1825fa5bf12e95","tid":1814913,"uid":49575,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T06:48:03.000Z","msg":"好多外國人有middle name添<br />\nJohnny John Johnson"},{"pid":"aa7a131d778e4f9674c87d353adf3a30b436daf0","tid":1814913,"uid":269269,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:09:14.000Z","msg":"所以係財經台？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f6d61035a5c447e4a8b933de7e042fea72d373e4","tid":1814913,"uid":66242,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:13:26.000Z","msg":"你搞清楚先<br />\n香港唔係非英語國家"},{"pid":"b8b0d00091d9f0bbf0ce093ef8998bd3f86bfac1","tid":1814913,"uid":130365,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:19:17.000Z","msg":"9成美國人都有middle name 即3個字<br />\nFirst middle last"},{"pid":"b849ff0085eeda4f6a8d6a2bd5c1e8e81ec05378","tid":1814913,"uid":66242,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:21:14.000Z","msg":"蘇軾，字子瞻，一字和仲，號東坡居士、鐵冠道人<br />\n杜甫，字子美，號少陵野老，一號杜陵野客、杜陵布衣<br />\n李白，字太白，號青蓮居士<br />\n韓愈，字退之，自稱郡望昌黎，世稱韓昌黎；晚年任吏部侍郎，又稱韓吏部。卒諡文，世稱韓文公<br />\n張居正，字叔大，號太嶽，又稱張江陵<br />\n孫中山，名文，幼名帝象，譜名德明，字明德、載之，號逸仙、日新。流亡日本時曾化名中山樵，故稱孫中山<br />\n蔣中正，原名瑞元，譜名周泰，學名志清，後改名中正，字介石<br />\n蔣經國，字建豐，一字存西<br />\n毛澤東，字潤之，筆名子任，曾化名李德勝<br />\n朱德，原名朱代珍，曾用名建德，字玉階"},{"pid":"b059b1c494f9482ead1193fe140cca52538560aa","tid":1814913,"uid":77143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:25:09.000Z","msg":"搞清楚，英文係香港official language<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Donald </span> <span style=\"color: blue;\">John </span> <span style=\"color: gold;\">Trump</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Carrie </span> <span style=\"color: gold;\">Lam </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">Cheng Yuet-ngor</span>"},{"pid":"54fc79637133591756f270c95ad3ff0f85e72f32","tid":1814913,"uid":66242,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:30:34.000Z","msg":"成日有人話咩某国人行不改名坐不改姓<br />\n肯定無讀過書唔識分姓名字號<br />\n古時姓下有氏<br />\n皇帝仲有尊號廟號諡號<br />\n今時都仲有人跟緊字輩啦"},{"pid":"e5ebf4377f04034a50ea71c7c6e542526cc049ee","tid":1814913,"uid":30836,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:30:55.000Z","msg":"台灣、馬拉、星加坡、香港、中國都有另取洋名嘅習俗"},{"pid":"6f7ae005691062a4830f7ddc22bbf19af0ee9b3e","tid":1814913,"uid":167289,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"b059b1c494f9482ead1193fe140cca52538560aa","tid":1814913,"uid":77143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:25:09.000Z","msg":"搞清楚，英文係香港official language<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Donald </span> <span style=\"color: blue;\">John </span> <span style=\"color: gold;\">Trump</span><br />\n<span style=\"color: blue;\">Carrie </span> <span style=\"color: gold;\">Lam </span> <span style=\"color: red;\">Cheng Yuet-ngor</span>"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-01-07T07:34:00.000Z","msg":"完全唔同喎<br />\n人哋first name, middle name, last name都係佢個名嘅一部份<br />\nCarrie有無寫落佢身份證我就唔知<br />\n但香港大部份人個英文名都係返學時老師叫佢改先改"},{"pid":"1